<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/baroness-sherlock> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Baroness Sherlock OBE was appointed as a Minister of State in the Department for Work and Pensions on 17 December 2024. She was previously Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State at the Department of Work and Pensions from 9 July 2024 to 17 December 2024."@en .
